delta - A syntax-highlighting pager for git and diff output
Installation:

 
 
# Download the latest delta release
wget https://github.com/dandavison/delta/releases/download/0.15.1/git-delta_0.15.1_amd64.deb

# Install the downloaded package
sudo dpkg -i git-delta_0.15.1_amd64.deb

# Fix any missing dependencies
sudo apt-get install -f -y
Basic Usage:

 
 
# Use delta to view git diffs
git diff | delta

# Configure git to use delta by default
git config --global core.pager "delta"
